Package: diva
Title: Swedish Research Publications Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Markus",
           family = "Skyttner",
           role = c("cre", "aut"),
           email = "markussk@kth.se")
Description: DiVA - an acronym for "Digitala Vetenskapliga Arkivet" -
    is a Swedish research publication database with national and institutional 
    portals available. This R package downloads and makes data available 
    to use from R.
